{"tid":1122801,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"復仇者聯盟4 時間解說","createTime":"2019-04-24T06:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T07:23:56.000Z","uid":195855,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"973cd9d2abfeaff70538be803c619abeab3d7a53","tid":1122801,"uid":195855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"設定：回到過去做任何野都唔會改變到佢地現有世界既事情 只會產生另一個平行宇宙 <br />\n例：回到過去殺死bb thones 唔會令佢地現有世界既事情改變 失去既人唔會番黎<br />\n<br />\n（對比：回去過去第一集 主角溝左自己老母既話自己都會消失 <br />\n依一個設定係過去發生既野改變左就會影響你現狀 ）（並非復4設定）<br />\n<br />\n要改變現狀只能係現有世界作出改變 就係用石變番一半人番黎。<br />\n<br />\n復4後 產生既平行宇宙：<br />\n1）2014 無左 thones 既世界 <br />\n2）Loki 偷左 魔方既世界 （有可能回歸番現有mcu 世界 ，個時間點 可以話 thor 之後捉番佢 因為權杖 ca 還番去 神盾局 不影響 奧創出現及英雄內戰）<br />\n<br />\nCa最後老左 佢係番左去現有mcu 既過去 睇住 另一個ca 解凍 可以end loop黎"},{"pid":"4c30f690312eded3a554a795d8213e4c807724de","tid":1122801,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:47:18.000Z","msg":"乜撚野係thones<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488f23af9c3172aa8662efd5596d2281eb1911b0","tid":1122801,"uid":195855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:48:56.000Z","msg":"Thanos<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8122bb2e8e233cb3cd4b74f7282c195a2ecd77ff","tid":1122801,"uid":15276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"btw除左時間石，我好想知其他石係要點還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c087508248254c2562cf99a67354d3ff3cf32825","tid":1122801,"uid":235391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T07:07:50.000Z","msg":"CA應該係用最後一枝紅色傳送藥返返去原本時空"},{"pid":"8083a47dea2b841afe73aa3a7267d9cfb8b0529e","tid":1122801,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c087508248254c2562cf99a67354d3ff3cf32825","tid":1122801,"uid":235391,"like":0,"dislike":0